message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit you based on its value of $12,000 to you. Considering its exceptional quality and the unique features it offers, I propose a price of $10,000 for this product. This price not only reflects its true value but also provides you with an opportunity to acquire it at a competitive rate compared to its market value. I look forward to your consideration and hope we can reach a mutually beneficial agreement.
